  <summary date="2025-02-28T18:47:37Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Local Access to Courts Act or LACA

This bill adds College Station to the list of places where court must be held in the Galveston Division of the Southern District of Texas.&#160;

Additionally, the bill adds El Centro to the list of places where court must be held in the Southern District of California.&#160;

